node.text: A poem by Boots O’Neil of the @6666ranch follow @6666supply house to see more of the legend who turns 90 in a couple weeks, but still rides everyday. We got to do a podcast with Boots last week at @trueburson house. Look out for it on YouTube, Spotify, and iTunes.
